## chart main Skillbox Project Status
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  vision["Vision: private single-tenant Tailnet/Docker dev box for one operator and coding agents"]
  green["GREEN Current proof-backed core: runtime graph, doctor/dev-sanity, pressure report, pulse, box inventory, skill visibility"]
  yellow["YELLOW Bead-covered validation and disk gates: skillbox-smart-20260518-validation-trust-gkn"]
  redClient["RED No active personal client in this checkout: no direct implementation Bead"]
  redMcp["RED MCP parity drift for Claude-only cm/dcg/fwc: no direct implementation Bead"]
  gray["GRAY Side-effecting infra paths not run: up, box-up, provision, teardown, worker launch"]
  next["Next: use h1k.2-h1k.5 to rank and mint implementation Beads for accepted gaps"]

  vision --> green
  vision --> yellow
  vision --> redClient
  vision --> redMcp
  vision --> gray
  yellow --> next
  redClient --> next
  redMcp --> next

  class green green
  class yellow yellow
  class redClient,redMcp red
  class gray gray
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
  classDef red fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c53030,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a0505
  classDef gray fill:#edf2f7,stroke:#718096,stroke-width:2px,color:#1a202c
```

## chart proof-status Proof Status
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  pass["GREEN Passed now: make doctor; make dev-sanity; render core; pressure-report; pulse status; box list; skills view; skill-audit"]
  warn["YELLOW Covered by skillbox-smart-20260518-validation-trust-gkn: broad unittest lane and disk-safe proof strategy"]
  disk["YELLOW Critical disk pressure: 1.6 GiB free, covered by skillbox-smart-20260518-validation-trust-gkn"]
  client["RED personal client unavailable: active_clients is empty and --client personal fails"]
  mcp["RED MCP parity drift: Claude-only cm/dcg/fwc not mirrored in Codex TOML"]
  infra["GRAY Not executed: runtime-up, up-surfaces, box-up, operator provision, teardown, worker launch"]

  pass --> warn
  pass --> disk
  warn --> client
  warn --> mcp
  pass --> infra

  class pass green
  class warn,disk yellow
  class client,mcp red
  class infra gray
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
  classDef red fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c53030,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a0505
  classDef gray fill:#edf2f7,stroke:#718096,stroke-width:2px,color:#1a202c
```

